OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Don
OL,4,CSheppard
OL,6,FMr Sheppard said: "We left from London
OL,7,Fdocks on an American liberty ship and
OL,8,Fjoined a convoy through the Straits of
OL,9,FDover.
OL,11,F"It was tough. We were being shelled
OL,12,Ffrom both sides and the boat behind us
OL,13,Fgot a direct hit from German artillery
OL,14,Fand they lost a lot of men."
OL,16,FHe transferred onto a landing craft to
OL,17,Fthe assembly area south of the Isle of
OL,18,FWight which was known as Piccadilly
OL,19,FCircus.
