OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Don
OL,4,CSheppard
OL,6,F"I was in a scout car - just me and
OL,7,Fthe driver. And a Bren gun on the
OL,8,Fturret just in case. He hit the water
OL,9,Fand we got soaking wet. The beach was
OL,10,Fcovered with Canadian dead.
OL,12,F"The most important thing was to get
OL,13,Foff the beach as quickly as possible
OL,14,Fbecause they were hitting the beach
OL,15,Fwith fire.
OL,17,F"We made our way towards the
OL,18,FCanadians, their target was Caen. They
OL,19,Fdidn't need our help and we made our
OL,20,Fway to Pegasus Bridge.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
