OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Don
OL,4,CSheppard
OL,6,F"It was a rough time, we took some
OL,7,Fcasualties there. We were in a wood
OL,8,Fand the Germans dive bombed us. I got
OL,9,Fwounded with shrapnel in the leg. We
OL,10,Fhad morphine to stab in for the pain.
OL,12,F"And we were hiding under a half track
OL,13,Fand someone said we better get out
OL,14,Fbecause it was loaded with explosives.
OL,16,F"We were all scared but when you are
OL,17,Fthat age you are all macho and don't
OL,18,Fshow it do you?
OL,20,F"I sit here now and say 'Why? Why did
OL,21,Fit happen?'
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
